                            >Looloo Technology</span
                        >,{" "}
                        <span class="font-medium text-white">AIMET</span>, and{
                            " "
                        }
                        <span class="font-medium text-white"
                            >Kasikorn Business-Technology Group</span
                        >.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        My work spans building robust APIs, deploying AI-powered
                        applications, crafting smart contracts, and contributing
                        to wellness tech solutions for medical students.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 space-y-2">
                        <li>
                            ðŸ¥ˆ Silver Medal at <span
                                class="font-medium text-white">iGEM 2024</span
                            >
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            ðŸ¥ˆ Silver Medal in <span
                                class="font-medium text-white"
                                >Super AI Engineer Season 3</span
                            >
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            ðŸ¥ˆ Silver Medal at the <span
                                class="font-medium text-white"
                                >17th Thailand Olympiad in Informatics</span
                            >
                        </li>
                    </ul>
